email.voterEmail:
Thanks for sending in your FPCA form to your local election office. Here is a copy for your records. 

**Please note this is an automated email from Vote From Abroad and not confirmation from your local election office.**

If you do not receive a confirmation of receipt from your local election office within 2 business days, please follow up with them directly: 

 {leoName} 

 Email: {leoEmail} 

 Phone: {leoPhone} 

 If you need any help, contact our volunteer voter support team at help@votefromabroad.org. 

